placement of Black's minor pieces. Black has very good control of the
important squares d5 and e5. Depending on the situation, the e7-knight can go
either to d5 or f5.}) 14... Be7 $11 {[%cal Gf6h5,Gh4e7,Gc6e7] We can now see
the point behind 13...h6. Black is planning to provoke exchanges by means of
