36. gxf3 Rxc4 $11) 31... Nd4 32. Rxf6 Kg7 33. Rfa6 Nxf3+ 34. Kf2 Rb3 35. Rxa7+
Kf6 36. R4a6+ Kf5 37. Rf7+ Ke4 38. gxf3+ Kd4 39. Ra2 $14 {Black is still
suffering in this rook endgame.}) 27. Bd1 Ne5 28. Bxa4 Qxa4 29. Qxa4 Bxa4 30.
Rxa4 f4 $1 (30... Rab8 31. Nxf5 (31. Rb1 Ng4 {1/2 (31) Yankelevich,L (2483)
-Berkes,F (2649) Gilleleje 2020}) 31... Rxb2 32. Rxa7 Rdd2 33. Rg7+ Kf8 34. Ra1
Ra2 35. Rxa2 Rxa2 36. Rxh7 Ng4 37. Rh8+ Kf7 38. Nh6+ Nxh6 39. Rxh6 Rc2 40. g4
$16) 31. c5 $1 {Improving Aronian's play} (31. Rxf4 Rd1+ 32. Rf1 Rxf1+ 33. Kxf1
Rb8 34. b4 Nxc4 35. Nf5 Rb5 36. g4 h5 37. h3 hxg4 38. hxg4 Ne5 $11 {1/2 (46)
Aronian,L (2765)-Caruana,F (2832) London 2018}) 31... fxe3 32. Rxe4 Rab8 33.
Rxe3 Rxb2 34. h3 Rc2 35. Rxf6 Rxc5 36. Ra6 $14 {It was a very deep preparation
from both sides. The position is objectively drawish but it's still not a 100%
