Nd2 e5 12. Bg5 Nd4 13. Qb1 Bf5 14. Bd3 Bxd3 15. Qxd3 Ne4 16. Ndxe4 {This move
seems to be the most natural one.} dxe4 17. Qd2 $1 {played among others by
